1
00:00:00,800 --> 00:00:04,240
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:06,150
From one fierce battle after another,

3
00:00:06,390 --> 00:00:10,850
we Alliance members had finally defeated 
all the members of Oracion Seis!

4
00:00:10,850 --> 00:00:17,530
But that triggered the seal on Brain's 
alternate personality, Master Zero, to unlock!

5
00:00:17,530 --> 00:00:19,300
What'll we do?!

6
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,510
I wonder for how long...

7
00:01:55,560 --> 00:02:02,250
How long will I be able to remain 
anchored at this harbor known as battle?

8
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:10,190
That's him!

9
00:02:15,230 --> 00:02:16,650
Jellal!

10
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:17,640
Wendy!

11
00:02:18,370 --> 00:02:20,430
You're safe? I'm glad.

12
00:02:20,670 --> 00:02:21,320
Yes.

13
00:02:24,170 --> 00:02:25,450
Jellal...

14
00:02:26,610 --> 00:02:27,690
Who are you?

15
00:02:32,790 --> 00:02:35,720
I knew it... He forgot...

16
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:42,380
Jellal's memories are all 
jumbled up right now.

17
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:48,560
He doesn't seem to remember about you, or me.

18
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,540
Memories?

19
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:59,760
I see... Then that's why...

20
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,310
From Pegasus to the Fairies!

21
00:03:09,970 --> 00:03:11,570
Wendy Marvel?

22
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:15,630
Did we know each other?

23
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:22,380
Please don't tell me you've also 
forgotten how to stop Nirvana...

24
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:24,010
W-Well...

25
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:34,940
A self-destruct magic circle 
will no longer work.

26
00:03:35,780 --> 00:03:37,880
I don't know of any other way...

27
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:39,900
I apologize.

28
00:03:42,270 --> 00:03:43,540
But...

29
00:03:43,990 --> 00:03:45,990
Hold it right there!

30
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:48,700
Then, what is going to happen to our guild?

31
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,850
It's right up ahead!

32
00:03:50,850 --> 00:03:52,380
If we don't stop it soon, then...

33
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:54,060
What's that?

34
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:39,420
What are you so afraid of? This is our fate.

35
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:44,220
Nabula! Punishment for our great sin...

36
00:04:53,770 --> 00:04:57,190
Everyone should just be destroyed!

37
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,080
That's...

38
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,240
Caitshelter!

39
00:05:04,610 --> 00:05:07,920
Don't tell me... This 
light... This magic power...

40
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,990
Nirvana is going to fire?!

41
00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:16,990
Oh, no!

42
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,960
Stop it!

43
00:05:43,530 --> 00:05:44,730
What?!

44
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:47,110
It missed!

45
00:05:59,050 --> 00:06:00,210
Something has...

46
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:06,750
Men! Men-men-men-men-men...

47
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,780
Ow.

48
00:06:09,470 --> 00:06:11,650
Nirvana's leg...

49
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:13,410
Who could have done this?

50
00:06:18,930 --> 00:06:19,810
That's...

51
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:31,670
The magical bomber, Christina!

52
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:33,070
It's on our side?

53
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,080
Can you hear me?

54
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:37,720
Somebody... Somebody, respond!

55
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:40,120
If you are safe, please respond!

56
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,440
That voice... Is that you, Hibiki?

57
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:45,920
Erza-san!

58
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,630
And you're safe too, I see, Wendy-chan.

59
00:06:48,810 --> 00:06:51,240
By the way, I'm safe as well...

60
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,470
Senpai! Thank goodness.

61
00:06:53,470 --> 00:06:57,910
What happened? I thought 
Christina was shot down...

62
00:06:58,330 --> 00:07:02,480
It was shot out of the sky like nothing by 
those guys near the entrance to the Woodsea.

63
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:05,360
So it could still fly?

64
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,760
Yeah... We managed, somehow.

65
00:07:08,490 --> 00:07:13,210
We're just a temporary alliance, so 
teamwork is all the more important.

66
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:20,410
Lyon is using his Creation magic to replace 
the wing that was destroyed from their attack.

67
00:07:21,350 --> 00:07:23,230
This is pretty tough...

68
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:26,460
The hull, which was split into pieces,

69
00:07:26,460 --> 00:07:31,760
is being held together by Sherry-san's 
Doll Attack and Ren's Air Magic.

70
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:36,500
I've never manipulated something so big!

71
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:39,020
Y-You call this h-heavy?

72
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:43,690
The attack from before was Eve's Snow Magic.

73
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:45,590
You guys...

74
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:51,900
I fused together the magic bombs 
that Christina had on board,

75
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:56,390
but all we could take out was one leg...

76
00:07:57,230 --> 00:08:00,950
It's... just that sturdy...

77
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:07,210
And... now... my magic power is...

78
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,460
Eve...

79
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:10,130
Eve, hang in there!

80
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:13,380
I'm not doing so well over here, either!

81
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:18,810
Not yet! A little more!

82
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:22,800
Everyone...

83
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,200
Thank you...

84
00:08:26,090 --> 00:08:28,900
Thank you, everyone!

85
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:35,690
As you can hear, we're reaching 
the limit of our magic power.

86
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:39,720
We can't attack from the ship any longer.

87
00:08:40,190 --> 00:08:44,370
And I don't know how long we'll 
be able to stay in the air.

88
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:47,110
Don't worry about us.

89
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:50,880
Just listen to this, before it's too late.

90
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:55,760
It took a long time, but I finally 
found it inside the Archive!

91
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,430
The way to stop Nirvana!

92
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,790
Really?

93
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:07,270
Nirvana has six leg-looking things, right?

94
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:13,860
They're actually more like pipes that suck 
up magic energy from the earth itself.

95
00:09:14,950 --> 00:09:20,400
The lacrima that regulate that absorption 
are located where the 6 legs join the main body.

96
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:26,370
If you destroy those 6 lacrima in 
different locations at the same time,

97
00:09:26,370 --> 00:09:29,130
Nirvana will be completely deactivated.

98
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,050
One at a time won't work.

99
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:36,110
The other lacrima will regenerate 
the one that was destroyed.

100
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:39,340
Destroy six lacrima in different 
places simultaneously?

101
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:40,850
But how?

102
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:44,740
I'd like to coordinate the timing...

103
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:49,600
But I don't think I can keep 
the telepathy up that long.

104
00:09:53,610 --> 00:09:58,530
I've uploaded the timing to your brains.

105
00:09:59,890 --> 00:10:01,030
20 minutes?

106
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:05,940
Nirvana is almost ready to fire again.

107
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:08,630
Six lacrima...

108
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,710
...at the same time...

109
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:10,770
...men.

110
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,210
I just know you all can do it!

111
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,880
I believe in you!

112
00:10:17,310 --> 00:10:18,930
Impossible!

113
00:10:19,470 --> 00:10:20,340
Who is that?

114
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:21,820
That voice...

115
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:23,300
It's the guy called Brain!

116
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:26,140
He's jacked my telepathy?

117
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:28,600
I am Zero!

118
00:10:28,850 --> 00:10:32,480
Zero... The Master of Oracion Seis!

119
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,940
Oracian Seis's master?

120
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:40,600
First, let me praise you.

121
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:46,540
I never thought there would be someone 
who could use Archive like Brain.

122
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:52,040
I see. So he knew about Nirvana 
because of his Archive.

123
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:55,290
Listen well, wizards of the light!

124
00:10:55,530 --> 00:10:59,720
Starting now, I will destroy everything!

125
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:04,000
As a start, I have destroyed 
three of your friends.

126
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:07,090
A Dragon Slayer...

127
00:11:07,090 --> 00:11:09,830
An Ice Creation Wizard...

128
00:11:09,830 --> 00:11:12,100
A Celestial Spirit Wizard!

129
00:11:12,890 --> 00:11:14,860
And maybe some cat, too...

130
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:16,320
Natsu and the others are...

131
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,570
That's got to be a lie!

132
00:11:17,570 --> 00:11:22,970
I believe you said something about 
destroying the lacrima at the same time?

133
00:11:23,570 --> 00:11:30,580
Right now, I am standing in front 
of one of those six lacrima!

134
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:39,630
As long as I am here, destroying all 
six at the same time is impossible!

135
00:11:41,970 --> 00:11:43,880
Zero has cut off his transmission...

136
00:11:45,850 --> 00:11:49,810
If we are going to destroy 
all six at the same time,

137
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:55,490
then we have no choice but to split 
up and each head to a different place.

138
00:11:57,610 --> 00:12:00,520
The chances of encountering Zero are 1 in 6.

139
00:12:00,950 --> 00:12:05,160
And what's more, unless it's you, Erza, 
there's no chance of winning against him.

140
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,500
Wait a second! What are you even saying?

141
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,950
We don't have six people!

142
00:12:08,950 --> 00:12:12,360
We don't have six wizards that 
could destroy the lacrima!

143
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:14,980
I...

144
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:19,430
...can't use any...

145
00:12:20,170 --> 00:12:21,610
...magic that can destroy!

146
00:12:21,610 --> 00:12:22,630
I'm sorry!

147
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,370
We have two here.

148
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:32,760
Is there no one else that can move?

149
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,190
My honey...

150
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,400
Am I not still here?

151
00:12:38,090 --> 00:12:39,690
Although I am tied up...

152
00:12:39,690 --> 00:12:41,070
Ichiya-san!

153
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:45,150
That makes... three.

154
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:50,690
Uh-oh! My magic power is... My 
telepathy is going to run out...

155
00:12:50,950 --> 00:12:54,340
We need three more! Someone answer me!

156
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:55,830
Is there no one else?

157
00:12:55,830 --> 00:12:57,800
Look! Christina is...

158
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,340
It's losing altitude!

159
00:13:05,570 --> 00:13:08,330
Damn it... I've run out of magic...

160
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:10,140
Pathetic...

161
00:13:11,230 --> 00:13:13,890
I'm... sorry.

162
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:17,940
Sherry!

163
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,440
Christina is crashing!

164
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:43,000
Gray...

165
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:46,140
Stand up...

166
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:52,610
You're a proud disciple of Ul!

167
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:56,140
You aren't going to lose 
to the likes of them!

168
00:13:59,900 --> 00:14:05,500
Lucy... I... really hate you.

169
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:11,520
Just 'cause you're a little 
cute, you think you're all that.

170
00:14:12,630 --> 00:14:16,260
Even though you're stupid 
and clumsy and a weakling...

171
00:14:17,050 --> 00:14:20,240
But how can I hate you if you die?

172
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:24,340
It wouldn't feel right... So answer me!

173
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:32,060
Natsu-san...

174
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,670
He-cat...

175
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,920
Natsu...

176
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:36,080
Can you hear our voices?

177
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:54,110
We... can... hear you...!

178
00:15:54,110 --> 00:15:55,330
Natsu-kun...

179
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:04,480
We'll destroy... all 
six... lacrima at once...

180
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,160
Men...

181
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:20,120
And a lucky one gets to fight 
Zero on the way, right?

182
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:23,430
There's only 18 minutes 
left... We have to hurry.

183
00:16:24,970 --> 00:16:28,310
We're gonna protect Carla and Wendy's guild!

184
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:37,590
My telepathy is going to run out soon.

185
00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:42,230
You should have a map in 
your brains that I sent you.

186
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:45,690
I numbered each of the lacrima.

187
00:16:46,470 --> 00:16:49,310
Decide on which one of you goes...

188
00:16:53,110 --> 00:16:57,200
Sherry... You try too hard.

189
00:17:05,290 --> 00:17:06,210
One!

190
00:17:06,210 --> 00:17:07,160
Two!

191
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,360
I'll go to three!

192
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:10,340
I just hope Zero's not there!

193
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:12,420
I will head to four.

194
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:16,050
My parfum tells me that it 
is the closest one to me.

195
00:17:16,050 --> 00:17:18,130
The map is what told you.

196
00:17:18,130 --> 00:17:21,550
Was it really necessary to correct me?

197
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:22,930
I'll take five.

198
00:17:22,930 --> 00:17:25,310
Erza! You doing okay?

199
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:28,890
Yeah... Thanks to her.

200
00:17:29,190 --> 00:17:30,710
Then, I'll...

201
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,610
You're six.

202
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:34,410
Was there someone else?

203
00:17:34,410 --> 00:17:35,490
Who was that just now?

204
00:17:36,130 --> 00:17:38,460
Natsu doesn't know about 
your circumstances yet.

205
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:41,540
He thinks you're an enemy. Don't speak.

206
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,680
Hey!

207
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:50,380
The telepathy cut off...

208
00:17:50,610 --> 00:17:53,000
He was at his limit...

209
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:58,940
That makes six.

210
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,050
We have to hurry!

211
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:06,810
Anyway, it sounds like we have six people.

212
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:11,520
Let's go! Whoever runs into Zero 
is responsible for defeating him!

213
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:14,780
Everyone has their own place 
to go, so there's no backup!

214
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:24,490
Men! Men! Men! Men!

215
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:30,720
Four! I am going to four!

216
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:34,910
Everyone is counting on me!

217
00:18:35,230 --> 00:18:38,380
I cannot betray that trust, no matter what!

218
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:43,210
I don't have time to catch my breath!

219
00:18:43,210 --> 00:18:46,390
I am still young! Men! Men!

220
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:14,410
Still alive, are we?

221
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:20,170
What'd you come here for, you little brat?

222
00:19:22,450 --> 00:19:25,080
Will it be you who breaks, or me?

223
00:19:25,910 --> 00:19:27,860
Let's find out!

224
00:19:28,970 --> 00:19:31,020
I think Zero is at number one.

225
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:32,270
Where Natsu-san is going!

226
00:19:33,770 --> 00:19:35,350
He has a good nose.

227
00:19:35,770 --> 00:19:37,690
He chose one for that reason.

228
00:19:37,690 --> 00:19:39,860
Then let's go and give him backup!

229
00:19:39,860 --> 00:19:41,020
If we all fight together, then...

230
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:42,470
Don't underestimate Natsu.

231
00:19:43,670 --> 00:19:46,740
Leave everything to him and we'll be fine.

232
00:19:49,290 --> 00:19:51,460
Na...tsu...?

233
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:54,030
We need to head to our destination!

234
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:56,380
I'm five. You're six, Jellal.

235
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:01,890
Jellal...

236
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:06,610
No... It's nothing...

237
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:22,280
Natsu Dragneel...

238
00:20:41,130 --> 00:20:43,590
You move better than you did before...

239
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:47,760
Dark Capriccio!

240
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:52,530
Don't think I'm on the same level as Brain.

241
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:07,740
Which one of us will break, you say?

242
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:13,950
It'll be <i>you</i>, obviously!

243
00:21:15,410 --> 00:21:19,160
Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!

244
00:21:35,730 --> 00:21:39,600
You're able to stop piercing 
magic... Interesting.

245
00:21:45,150 --> 00:21:46,320
Who is it?

246
00:21:59,900 --> 00:22:01,570
Jellal!

247
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:07,140
Did your memories return?

248
00:23:55,670 --> 00:24:00,090
We know how to stop Nirvana, 
so it's time to cut loose!

249
00:24:00,090 --> 00:24:01,270
Aye!

250
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:03,490
But everyone's all beat up...

251
00:24:03,490 --> 00:24:06,220
Nobody has the energy to cut loose anymore...

252
00:24:06,220 --> 00:24:07,540
That's where spirit kicks in!

253
00:24:07,540 --> 00:24:10,100
Yeah! I'm all fired up!

254
00:24:10,100 --> 00:24:13,510
Just this one time, I'm jealous 
of your simplicity, Natsu.

255
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:16,510
Next time: The Power of Memories!

256
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:18,930
Don't you want to show 
Carla how cool you can be?

257
00:24:18,930 --> 00:24:20,680
I'm gettin' fired up!

258
00:24:22,020 --> 00:24:24,600
Now who's the simple-minded one?

259
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:26,930


